    • Method Detail

      • create

        public static TagRelation create(Long id,
                                 Long tagId,
                                 String containerId)
        Factory method to create an instance from the Interface TagRelation.

        The usage from the fluent builder TagRelationBuilder is preferred against the directly usage from this method.

        • All attributes are mandory and validate against DefaultTagValidator.
        • The attribute id defines the id from the entity.
        • The attribute tagId defines the id from the Tag.
        • The attribute containerId defines the id from the container where the Tag should be shown.
        Parameters:
        id - The id (mandory attribute) from this DefaultTagRelation.
        tagId - The tagId (mandory attribute) from this DefaultTagRelation.
        containerId - The containerId (mandory attribute) from this DefaultTagRelation.
        Returns:
        A new instance from the Interface TagRelation.
        Since:
        0.1.0
        See Also:
        TagRelation, TagRelationBuilder, DefaultTagValidator
